file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: OpenApi Petstoe
servers:
  - url: http://petstore.{host}.io/v1
    description: The production API server
    variables:
      host:
        default: openapi
paths:
  /ping:
    get:
      operationId: operation_get_/ping
      parameters:
        - name: x-client
          in: header
          schema:
            type: string
            default: "foo"
          required: true
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Ok
